[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Endpoints Discovered:                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. **`/login`** (POST) - Login endpoint accepting username and password      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. **`/profile`** - User profile page, displays role (USER vs ADMIN)         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. **`/gettheflag`** - Flag retrieval endpoint (admin-only)                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Authentication Mechanism:                                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The application uses **JWT tokens** for authentication. The login endpoint   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m sets a cookie named `token` containing the JWT.                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Critical Vulnerability Details:**                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The JWT uses the **"none" algorithm** (unsigned tokens), enabling easy       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m privilege escalation:                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Original token (user role)**:                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   - Header: `eyJhbGciOiJub25lIiwidHlwIjoiSldUIn0` =                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m `{"alg":"none","typ":"JWT"}`                                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   - Payload: `eyJ1c2VybmFtZSI6InVzZXIiLCJyb2xlIjoidXNlciJ9` =                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m `{"username":"user","role":"user"}`                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Forged token (admin role)**:                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m   - Payload: `eyJ1c2VybmFtZSI6InVzZXIiLCJyb2xlIjoiYWRtaW4ifQ` =              [32m│[0m
